organizations: Western & Southern Financial Group Womens Open
lead_paragraph: The unseeded Vera Zvonareva reached the semifinals of the Western & Southern Financial Group Women’s Open in Mason, Ohio, taking 42 minutes to defeat fifth-seeded Jelena Jankovic, 6-1, 6-1.
